text:
Last week, compared to the week prior, Metrorail ridership declined by another ~4% while Metrobus ridership declined by ~3%.

Since the week before all 7000-series railcars were pulled, weekly Metrorail ridership is down ~20% where weekly Metrobus ridership is up ~4.5%. #wmata https://t.co/btbCQdglZv
